N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 2 ยง 7.12 - Orders shall be to specific dealers

State Regulations

Purchase orders not executed to a specified manufacturer or
dealer are regarded as blanket requests and shall not be
accepted. Notes
